Department Table:  Primary Key:- DeptId
                   Candidate Key:- DName
                   Foreign Key:- HODId(InstrId  From Instructor Table)

Instructor Table:   Primary Key:- InstrId
                    Candidate Key:- Name, Email
                    Foreign Key:- DeptId

Course table:   Primary Key:- CId
                Candidate Key:- CName
                Foreign Key:- Null

Allocation:   Primary Key:-CId+InstrId(Composite)
              Candidate Key:- Null
              Foreign Key:-Cid, InstrId
